<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.1.5">
<l>pāreḻu kaṭaleḻu malaiyeḻumāyc</l>
<l>cīrkeḻu mivvula kēḻumellām</l>
<l>ārkeḻu vayiṟṟiṉi laṭakkiniṉṟaṅ</l>
<l>kōreḻut tōruru vāṉavaṉē</l>
<l rend="indent">āṇṭāyuṉaik kāṇpatō raruḷeṉak karuḷutiyēl,</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṇṭēṉmaṉai vāḻkkaiyai viṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who became the one form of the one letter,</l>
<l>Having remained there, compressing into [your] stomach, filled full,</l>
<l>The whole of these seven worlds, filled with excellence,</l>
<l>Being the seven earths, seven seas, and seven mountains,</l>
<l rend="indent">Master, if you bless me with the one blessing of seeing you,</l>
<l rend="indent">I would not want this domestic life, you who dwells in Viṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
